- [ ] Axios used for HTTP requests
- [ ] Proper error handling with try/catch
- [ ] Auth tokens handled by interceptors
- [ ] Type-safe API function signatures

## User Experience

### Notifications
- [ ] Sonner toasts used for all notifications
